{"kanda":6,"sarga":119,"description":"","verses":[{"v":1,"dev":"एवमुक्तातुवैदेहिपरुषंरोमहर्षणम् ।राघवेणसरोषेणश्रुत्वाप्रव्यथिताऽभवत्","trans":"Vaidehi heard the harsh horripilating words spoken by Rama in anger and was very much afflicted.","words":[{"d":"सरोषेण","m":"in anger"},{"d":"राघवेण","m":"by Raghava"},{"d":"एवम्","m":"in that way"},{"d":"परुषम्","m":"harsh"},{"d":"रोमहर्षणम्","m":"horripilating"},{"d":"उक्ता","m":"spoken"},{"d":"वैदेहि","m":"Vaidehi"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"having heard"},{"d":"प्रव्यथिता","m":"afflicted"},{"d":"अभवत्","m":"became"}]},{"v":2,"dev":"सातदश्रुतपूर्वंहिजनेमहतिमैथिली ।श्रुत्वाभर्तृर्वचोरूक्षंलज्जयावनताभवत्","trans":"Then Mythili hearing her husband 's harsh words, in the presence of a large number of people, stayed bent with shyness.","words":[{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"सामैथिली","m":"she, Mythili"},{"d":"महति","m":"large number"},{"d":"जने","m":"people"},{"d":"अश्रुतपूर्वम्","m":"filled with tears"},{"d":"घोरम्","m":"ruthless"},{"d":"भर्तुः","m":"husband 's"},{"d":"श्रुत्वा","m":"hearing"},{"d":"लज्जया","m":"shy"},{"d":"अवनता","m":"bent"},{"d":"अभवत्","m":"stayed"}]},{"v":3,"dev":"प्रविशन्तीवगात्राणिस्वानिसाजनकात्मजा ।वाक्षरैस्स्सैःसशल्येवभृशमाश्रूण्यवर्तयत्","trans":"As if pierced by those arrowlike words, Janaka's daughter shed tears excessively, shrinking into her own limbs.","words":[{"d":"साजनकात्मजा","m":"she Janaka's daughter"},{"d":"स्वानि","m":"her own"},{"d":"गात्राणि","m":"limbs"},{"d":"प्रविशन्तीव","m":"shrinking"},{"d":"चाक्षरैः","m":"from eyes"},{"d":"सशल्येव","m":"by the arrows"},{"d":"भृशम्","m":"excessively"},{"d":"अश्रूणि","m":"tears"},{"d":"अवर्तयत्","m":"shed"}]},{"v":4,"dev":"ततोबाष्पपरिक्लिन्नंप्रमार्जन्तीस्वमाननम् ।शनैर्गद्गदयावाचाभर्तारमिदमब्रवीत्","trans":"Thereafter, wiping her face clean from flowing tears she spoke slowly in a choked voice in broken words to her husband.","words":[{"d":"ततः","m":"thereafter"},{"d":"बाष्पपरिक्लिन्नम्","m":"flowing tears clean"},{"d":"स्वम्","m":"her"},{"d":"आननम्","m":"face"},{"d":"प्रमार्जन्ती","m":"wiping off"},{"d":"भर्तारम्","m":"to husband"},{"d":"गद्गदया","m":"in broken tone"},{"d":"वाचा","m":"words"},{"d":"शनैः","m":"slowly"},{"d":"इदम्","m":"thus"},{"d":"अब्रवीत्","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":5,"dev":"किंमामसदृशंवाक्यमीदृशंश्रोत्रदारुणम् ।रूक्षंश्रावयसेवीर प्राकृतःप्राकृतमिव","trans":"\"Hero! Why are you addressing me in such harsh unkind words in a rude manner, in a harsh tone like a common man?\"","words":[{"d":"वीर","m":"hero"},{"d":"माम्","m":"me"},{"d":"प्राकृतः","m":"address"},{"d":"प्राकृतामिव","m":"like a common man"},{"d":"माम्","m":"to me"},{"d":"असदृशम्","m":"unkind"},{"d":"ईदृशब्","m":"this kind of tone"},{"d":"श्रोत्रदारुणम्","m":"harsh to hear"},{"d":"रूक्षम्","m":"rude"},{"d":"वाक्यम्","m":"words"},{"d":"किम्","m":"why"},{"d":"श्रावयसे","m":"speaking"}]},{"v":6,"dev":"न तथास्मिमहाबाहो यथामामवगच्छसि ।प्रत्ययंगच्छमेस्वेनचारित्रेणैवतेशपे","trans":"\"O Mighty armed! I am not as you think of me, so also show me a proof of it in my past. I swear on my past.\"","words":[{"d":"महाबाहो","m":"mighty armed"},{"d":"माम्","m":"me"},{"d":"यथा","m":"similarly"},{"d":"अवगच्छसि","m":"not as you think of me"},{"d":"तथा","m":"so also"},{"d":"मे","m":"my"},{"d":"प्रत्ययम्","m":"proof"},{"d":"गच्छ","m":"period"},{"d":"स्वेन","m":"myself"},{"d":"चारित्रेण","m":"my past"},{"d":"ते","m":"to you"},{"d":"शपे","m":"vow"}]},{"v":7,"dev":"पृथकस्त्रीणांप्रचारेणजातिंत्वंपरिशङ्कसे ।परित्यजैनांशङ्कांतुयदितेऽहंपरीक्षिता","trans":"\"You give up judging all womankind by the path followed by vulgar women. You give up these doubts if you have examined.\"","words":[{"d":"पृथकस्त्रीणां","m":"vulgar women"},{"d":"प्रचारेण","m":"extending"},{"d":"त्वम्","m":"you"},{"d":"जातिम्","m":"race"},{"d":"परिशङ्कसे","m":"doubting"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"ते","m":"to you"},{"d":"परीक्षितायदि","m":"if you have examined"},{"d":"एनाम्","m":"these"},{"d":"शङ्काम्","m":"doubts"},{"d":"परित्यज","m":"give up"}]},{"v":8,"dev":"यदहंगात्रसम्पर्शंगतास्मिविशवाप्रभो ।कामकारो न मेतत्रदैवंतत्रापराध्यति","trans":"\"O Lord! I was helpless when Ravana contacted my limbs in the past. I was not acting according to my will. My fate is to be blamed and not me.\"","words":[{"d":"प्रभो","m":"Lord"},{"d":"विवशा","m":"helpless"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I am"},{"d":"गात्रसम्पर्शम्","m":"touching the limbs"},{"d":"गता","m":"in the past"},{"d":"अस्मि","m":"by me"},{"d":"इतियत्","m":"all this"},{"d":"तत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"मे","m":"to me"},{"d":"कामकारः","m":"acting at will"},{"d":"न","m":"not"},{"d":"तत्र","m":"there"},{"d":"दैवम्","m":"fate"},{"d":"अपराध्यति","m":"to be blamed"}]},{"v":9,"dev":"मदधीनंतुयत्तन्मेहृदयंत्वयिवर्तते ।पराधीनेषुगात्रेषुकिंकरिष्याम्यनीश्वरी","trans":"\"That mind which is under my control is my heart and it abides in you. What can I do about my limbs when I am at others' mercy?\"","words":[{"d":"यत्","m":"that which"},{"d":"मदधीनम्","m":"mind under my control"},{"d":"तत्","m":"that"},{"d":"मे","m":"is my"},{"d":"हृदयंतु","m":"heart"},{"d":"त्वयि","m":"you"},{"d":"वर्तते","m":"abides"},{"d":"पराधीनेषु","m":"at others' mercy"},{"d":"गात्रेषु","m":"limbs"},{"d":"अनीश्वरी","m":"not possible"},{"d":"किम्","m":"what"},{"d":"करिष्यामि","m":"can I do"}]},{"v":10,"dev":"सहसम्वृद्धभावेनसंसर्गेण च मानद ।यदितेऽहं न विज्ञाताहतातेनास्मिशाश्वतम्","trans":"\"Honourable Rama! If I am not understood by you despite our growing up together with love and in spite of our intimate relationship, I am done forever.\"","words":[{"d":"मानद","m":"honourable"},{"d":"सहसम्वृद्धभावेन","m":"by our growing up together with love"},{"d":"संसर्गेणच","m":"our intimate relationship"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"ते","m":"to you"},{"d":"न विज्ञातायदि","m":"if I am not known"},{"d":"तेन","m":"by you"},{"d":"शाश्वतम्","m":"permanently"},{"d":"हताअस्मि","m":"I am done"}]},{"v":11,"dev":"प्रेषितस्तेमहावीरोहनुमानवलोककः ।लङ्कास्थाहंत्वयाराजन्किंतदा न विसर्जिता","trans":"\"King! When the great hero Hanuman was sent by you to find me in Lanka, why did you not leave me then.\"","words":[{"d":"राजन्","m":"king"},{"d":"महावीरः","m":"great hero"},{"d":"हनुमान्","m":"Hanuman"},{"d":"अवलोककः","m":"to find"},{"d":"ते","m":"by you"},{"d":"प्रेषितः","m":"sent"},{"d":"लङ्कास्था","m":"in Lanka"},{"d":"अहम्","m":"I"},{"d":"त्वया","m":"by you"},{"d":"तदा","m":"then"},{"d":"किम्","m":"why"},{"d":"न विसर्जिता","m":"did you not leave"}]},{"v":12,"dev":"प्रत्यक्षंवानरस्यास्यतद्वाक्यसमनन्तरम् ।त्वयासन्त्यक्तयावीरत्यक्तंस्याजजीवितंमया","trans":"\"O hero! Had you given me up immediately on receiving your message from Vanara I would have given up my life in the presence of Hanuman there itself.\"","words":[{"d":"वीर","m":"heroic"},{"d":"अस्य","m":"your"},{"d":"वानरस्य","m":"with Vanara"},{"d":"प्रत्यक्षम्","m":"in his presence"},{"d":"तद्वाक्यसमनन्तरम्","m":"after your message"},{"d":"त्वया","m":"by you"},{"d":"मया","m":"by me"},{"d":"जीवितम्","m":"life"},{"d":"त्यक्तम्","m":"given up"},{"d":"स्यात्","m":"there itself"}]},{"v":13,"dev":"न वृथातेश्रमोऽयंस्यात्संशयेन्यस्यजीवितम् ।सुहृज्जनपरिक्लेशो न चायंविपुलस्तव","trans":"\"O Life! If you had a doubt this exertion to you is wasteful. This fruitless hard work was perhaps not required on your part nor your friends.\"","words":[{"d":"जीवितम्","m":"life"},{"d":"संशये","m":"doubt"},{"d":"न्यस्य","m":"exertion"},{"d":"ते","m":"to you"},{"d":"वृधा","m":"wasteful"},{"d":"अयंश्रमः","m":"this hard work"},{"d":"न स्यात्","m":"perhaps not required"},{"d":"अयम्","m":"this"},{"d":"विफलः","m":"failure"},{"d":"तव","m":"your"},{"d":"सुहृज्जनपरिक्लेशः","m":"nor your friends"},{"d":"न च","m":"and not"}]},{"v":14,"dev":"त्वयातुनृपशार्दूलदोषमेवानुवर्तता ।लघुनेवमनुष्येणस्त्रीत्वमेवपुरस्कृतम्","trans":"\"O tiger among kings! You also gave up yourself to anger like a weak man and adopted womanliness\"","words":[{"d":"नृपशार्दूल","m":"tiger among kings"},{"d":"रोषमेव","m":"gave yourself to anger"},{"d":"अनुवर्तता","m":"following"},{"d":"त्वयातु","m":"you also"},{"d":"लघुना","m":"weak"},{"d":"मनुष्येणइव","m":"like a man"},{"d":"स्त्रीत्वमेव","m":"womanliness"},{"d":"प पुरस्कृतम्","m":"adopting"}]},{"v":15,"dev":"अपदेशेनजनकादुत्पततिर्वसुथातलात् ।ममवृत्तं च वृत्तज्ञबहुते न पुरस्कृतम्","trans":"","words":[{"d":"वृत्तज्ञ","m":"divine birth"},{"d":"अपदेशेव","m":"mentioned"},{"d":"जनकात्","m":"birth"},{"d":"वसुधातलात्","m":"in the ground"},{"d":"उत्पततिः","m":"risen"},{"d":"मम","m":"me"},{"d":"बहु","m":"many"},{"d":"वृत्तं च","m":"divine origin"},{"d":"ते","m":"you"},{"d":"पुरस्कृतम्","m":"considered"}]},{"v":16,"dev":"न प्रमाणीकृतंपाणिर्भाल्येममनिपीडितः ।ममभक्तिश्चशीलं च सर्वंतेपृष्ठतःकृतम्","trans":"\"When in my young age you held my hand as a mark of acceptance (in our marriage), has it not been considered by you? Has my devotion, character and chastity not been taken into account?\"","words":[{"d":"बाल्ये","m":"young"},{"d":"निपीडितः","m":"pressed"},{"d":"ममपाणिः","m":"my hand"},{"d":"न प्रमाणीकृतः","m":"as a mark of acceptance"},{"d":"मम","m":"my"},{"d":"भक्तिश्च","m":"with devotion"},{"d":"शीलं च","m":"my character"},{"d":"सर्वम्","m":"all"},{"d":"ते","m":"to you"},{"d":"पृष्ठतः","m":"chastity"},{"d":"कृतम्","m":"not taken into account"}]},{"v":17,"dev":"इतिब्रुवन्तीरुदतीबाष्पगद्गगभाषिणी ।उवाचलक्ष्मणंसीतादीनंध्यानपरायणम्","trans":"Thus speaking, and weeping with tears, with choked throat, Sita was absorbed in her mind and piteous. She spoke to Lakshmana.","words":[{"d":"इति","m":"thus"},{"d":"बृवन्ती","m":"speaking"},{"d":"रूदती","m":"weeping"},{"d":"बाष्पगद्गदभाषिणी","m":"with tears and choked throat"},{"d":"सीता","m":"Sita"},{"d":"दीनम्","m":"piteous"},{"d":"ध्यानपरायणम्","m":"absorbed in mind"},{"d":"लक्ष्मणम्","m":"Lakshmana"},{"d":"उवाच","m":"spoke"}]},{"v":18,"dev":"चितांमेकुरुसौमित्रेव्यवनस्यास्यभेषजम् ।मिध्यापवादोपहतानाहंजीवितुमुत्सहे","trans":"\"Saumithri! Cure for this sorrow is only pyre. Arrange for pyre as I do not desire to live with false reproaches.\"","words":[{"d":"सौमित्रे","m":"Saumithri"},{"d":"मे","m":"I"},{"d":"अस्य","m":"this"},{"d":"व्यसनस्य","m":"sorrow"},{"d":"भेषजम्","m":