 eyed Sita descending on the golden altar, into the fire like goddess of fortune descending on her vehicle.","words":[{"d":"विशालाक्षीम्","m":"large eyed goddess of fortune"},{"d":"हन्यवाहनम्","m":"on her vehicle"},{"d":"पतन्तीम्","m":"descending"},{"d":"रुक्मवेदिनिभाम्","m":"golden altar"},{"d":"तांसीताम्","m":"her, Sita"},{"d":"सर्वाणि","m":"all beings"},{"d":"रूपाणि","m":"forms"},{"d":"ददृशुः","m":"witnessed"}]},{"v":33,"dev":"ददृशुस्तांमहाभागांप्रविशन्तींहुताशनम् सीतांकृत्स्नास्त्रयोलोकाःपुण्यामाज्याहुतीमिव ।","trans":"All the three worlds witnessed noble dark Sita entering the fire, like ghee offered to fire.","words":[{"d":"हुताशनम्","m":"fire"},{"d":"प्रविशन्तीम्","m":"entering"},{"d":"महाभागाम्","m":"noble"},{"d":"तांसीताम्","m":"Sita"},{"d":"कृत्स्नाः","m":"dark"},{"d":"त्रयः","m":"three"},{"d":"लोकाः","m":"worlds"},{"d":"पुण्याम्","m":"blessed"},{"d":"आज्याहुतीमिव","m":"like ghee offered to fire"},{"d":"ददृशुः","m":"witnessed"}]},{"v":34,"dev":"प्रचुक्रुशुःस्त्रियःसर्वास्तांदृष्टवाहव्यवाहवे पतन्तींसंस्कृतांमन्रन्स्सैर्वसोर्दारामिवाध्वरे ।","trans":"All the women who stood there fled, screaming on seeing Sita falling into fire, like the flow of ghee poured continuously into sacrificial fire reciting sacred verses by priests.","words":[{"d":"अध्वरे","m":"priests"},{"d":"मन्स्सरैः","m":"recitation of sacred verses"},{"d":"संस्कृताम्","m":"traditionally"},{"d":"वसोः","m":"dwelling there"},{"d":"धारामिव","m":"like the flow"},{"d":"हव्यवाहवे","m":"in sacrificial fire"},{"d":"पतन्तीम्","m":"falling"},{"d":"ताम्","m":"her"},{"d":"दृष्टवा","m":"seeing"},{"d":"सर्वाः","m":"all"}]},{"v":35,"dev":"ददृशुस्तांत्रयोलोकादेवगन्धर्वदानवाः शस्तांपतन्तींनिरयेत्रिविवाद्धेवतामिव ।","trans":"All the Devas, Gandharvas and Danavas of the three worlds who witnessed her falling, extolled her as if goddess was falling from heaven into hell.","words":[{"d":"त्रयः","m":"three"},{"d":"लोकाः","m":"worlds"},{"d":"देवगन्धर्वदानवाः","m":"Devas, Gandharvas and Danavas"},{"d":"शस्ताम्","m":"e